{"tid":1269063,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"堅持住呀咁多位香港人！！！！","createTime":"2019-06-30T12:37:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T12:47:45.000Z","uid":68708,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"febc2b8610a990d6c6e3c845096187656fc82467","tid":1269063,"uid":68708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T12:37:35.000Z","msg":"呢段時間大家都可能好攰同沮喪 今個6月的確感覺過得好漫長<br />\n<br />\n我自己係呢一個月變左唔少。 以往可能只係識係fb/ig po野當支持左，變成成個6月都發過唔少次夢親身去左現場 亦都係夢境入面食左唔少彈<br />\n<br />\n見身邊唔少朋友已經打算移民。 相信唔少人都有呢個諗法！但係我真係唔想眼白白見住自己出世同成長既地方慢慢被蠶食<br />\n<br />\n希望大家真係唔好放棄！香港人從來都係有希望既一群！<br />\n<br />\n聽日應該都係自己去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望見到大家。<br />\n聽日見！！"},{"pid":"d2ed71ff9e70844171a96cfe1341b6d83faabc01","tid":1269063,"uid":68708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T12:37:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba05f367c4a1e6f79f444527a87735f60ccd176a","tid":1269063,"uid":68708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T12:38:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />聽日見"},{"pid":"d0deafd37fb98009a476392cace9eec06ab48e24","tid":1269063,"uid":124859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T12:38:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">七一野餐會 <br />\n人數決定一切</span></span><br />\n<br />\n&mdash; 唔 理 衝 唔 衝 ， 迫 爆 金 紫 荊 VER 2 &mdash;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1267041\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1267041</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n630/71］71朝早08:00升旗 請6月30晚出黎煲底留守 否則太遲啦<br />\n<a href=\"http